  "text": "From another perspectives, there are other on-going research works in this area. For instance, designing a satellite-based antenna system operating in the Ka band between the UAV and the remote pilot have been studied in [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . The proposed onboard satellite antennas designed for UAVs are low-profile and broadband antennas that are very small in dimensions and operate in a wide range of frequency spectrum. These two main features are very useful and essential for designing small UAVs.",
